messages.message:
I think the main thing here is that we recently changed how we select projects to open - previously we had the sidebar, then we did the app UX refresh and put project selection in the nav bar at the top, and now we want to direct people to Workspaces.
In the first two, the user can select whatever project that they want (for example, maybe one in a shared workspace), even if they end up in this "create project" landing page, but now there's not - they're basically forced to create a new project
@Paul H I think you made those last changes, do you have any thoughts?
